title: Dating Anxiety with Tank Sinatra! | Chris Distefano Presents: Chrissy Chaos | EP 4
description:
This episode Chris has on his FIRST guest Tank Sinatra aka Tanks Good News on social media! They talk Bitcoin, book lists and fashion, Vinny helps Tank with a haircut, RIP Rush Limbaugh, Tank read about Malcom X, Slug anatomy, This week Chris and Tank talk about law 4 from The 48 Laws of Power, Say Less!, be careful with sarcasm, Tank used this book for Dating life, being paranoid that your partner is cheating on you, Chris and Vinny talk about cheating anxiety, boys talk Parables, Chrissy Histories gets WILD, how to travel across the country the right way, Tank helps Chris move a dresser to the garbage. CHAOS!
